OL,3,CApproached by 20 men in two hours:
OL,4,CReality of being a woman alone at night
OL,6,FCree Haughton tried walking alone on a
OL,7,Fbusy street at night to see what would
OL,8,Fhappen
OL,10,FAs a young woman, I'm all too familiar
OL,11,Fwith the challenges we have to face to
OL,12,Fkeep ourselves safe.
OL,14,FGiven my lived experience, it wasn't
OL,15,Fsurprising to me when our survey
OL,16,Fexposed how scared the majority of us
OL,17,Ffeel in various aspects of life.
OL,19,FEarlier this year, ITV News
OL,20,Finterviewed more than 1,000 young
OL,21,Fadults.
