OL,3,CApproached by 20 men in two hours:
OL,4,CReality of being a woman alone at night
OL,6,FOur report found that more than eight
OL,7,Fout of 10 young women feel unsafe
OL,8,Fwalking home alone in the dark.
OL,10,FAnd more than six out of 10 feel
OL,11,Funsafe on their own in a bar.
OL,13,FThe sad reality is that when I saw the
OL,14,Fresults, I expected the numbers to be
OL,15,Fhigher.
OL,17,FI wanted to demonstrate, in a real and
OL,18,Ftangible way, what it can be like when
OL,19,Fyou are alone as a young woman at
OL,20,Fnight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
