OL,3,CApproached by 20 men in two hours:
OL,4,CReality of being a woman alone at night
OL,6,FTo do this, we used a secret camera
OL,7,Fattached to me, two producers who were
OL,8,Falso filming and a security guard
OL,9,Fwatching over the whole thing for our
OL,10,Fsafety.
OL,12,FI walked alone on a busy Cardiff
OL,13,Fstreet at night in a vulnerable
OL,14,Fsituation to see who would offer me
OL,15,Fhelp.
OL,17,FI was approached by men 20 times in
OL,18,Fjust two hours.
OL,20,FMy cover story for them was that I was
OL,21,Flooking for my friends.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
