OL,3,CApproached by 20 men in two hours:
OL,4,CReality of being a woman alone at night
OL,6,FThe vast majority of the men
OL,7,Fresponded: "I'll be your friend".
OL,9,FOut of all of these interactions, only
OL,10,Fone man offered to help me.
OL,12,FI chose Cardiff because South Wales
OL,13,FPolice Force had recently announced,
OL,14,Fthanks to a new initiative, a 30% drop
OL,15,Fin violence against women on the
OL,16,Fnightlife scene.
