OL,3,CApproached by 20 men in two hours:
OL,4,CReality of being a woman alone at night
OL,6,FI'm totally aware in this instance
OL,7,Fthat none of the interactions would
OL,8,Fhave warranted police intervention, in
OL,9,Ffact, some of them were quite pleasant
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,FBut I think what the exercise shows is
OL,13,Fthat it is not necessarily just the
OL,14,Fthreat of more serious sexual assaults
OL,15,Fthat make women feel unsafe.
OL,17,FThe fact that 19 out of 20 men used me
OL,18,Fbeing alone, lost and vulnerable as an
OL,19,Fopportunity to ask for my contact
OL,20,Fdetails, rather than to offer me help,
OL,21,Fis quite concerning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
