OL,3,CApproached by 20 men in two hours:
OL,4,CReality of being a woman alone at night
OL,6,FSome men even approached me with
OL,7,Fstrange requests: "Do you play tennis?
OL,8,FI will give you free lessons."
OL,10,FA lot of them did not respect my
OL,11,Fpersonal space.
OL,13,FAnd one man got annoyed when I
OL,14,Frejected his advances.
OL,16,FAlthough most of the interactions were
OL,17,Fharmless, the relentless nature of the
OL,18,Fapproaches when you are on your own is
OL,19,Fexhausting.
